All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AssetSetter
The AssetSetter class is responsible for initializing and placing game objects and zombies within the game world.
CollisionChecker
The CollisionChecker class is responsible for detecting and managing collisions between entities and tiles or objects within the game world.
Entity
Entity is an abstract representation of all moving objects within the game world, including the player, enemies, and NPCs.
EventHandler
The EventHandler class is responsible for managing events that occur within the game.
EventRect
EventRect extends the Rectangle class to include functionality for in-game events.
GamePanel
The GamePanel class serves as the main controller for the game.
KeyHandler
The KeyHandler class implements the KeyListener interface and handles all keyboard interactions for controlling the game state and player movement.
Main
The Main class serves as the entry point for the game application.
ObjectDoor
ObjectDoor representing doors on the map
ObjectHeart
ObjectHeart representing hearts for players' health to gather
ObjectKey
ObjectKey representing a key for players to gather in order to finish the game.
ObjectMed
ObjectMed representing a med pack to heal players
ObjectTrap
ObjectTrap representing a trap object to damage players
ObjectVaccine
ObjectVaccine representing a vaccine object to cure zombies and gain points
Player
The Player class represents the player-controlled character in the game.
Player.ObjectAction
 
Sound
The Sound class is responsible for loading and playing sound files.
SuperObject
SuperObject is the base class for all interactive objects in the game that can be drawn on the screen.
Tile
 
TileManager
 
UI
The UI class is responsible for rendering the game's user interface, including the HUD (Heads-Up Display), title screen, pause screen, settings screen, and game over screen.
UtilityTool
The UtilityTool class provides utility functions to manipulate images.
Zombie
The Zombie class extends the Entity class with properties and methods specific to zombies in the game.
